Package eu.advance.logistics.flow.engine

The Flow Engine main classes, the Flow Engine Compiler and the Flow Engine Configuration classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AdvanceSchemaResolver
    Interface for providing support to resolve a schema URI into an XType.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdvanceBlockResolver
    Class that locates and creates blocks based on their name.
    AdvanceCompiler
    The ADVANCE block compiler which turns the the flow description into runnable advance blocks.
    AdvanceEngineConfig
    The engine configuration record.
    AdvanceFlowEngine
    The Advance Data Flow Engine main program.
    AdvanceListenerConfig
    The listener configuration record for the engine.
    AdvanceLocalSchemaResolver
    Class to resolve schemas and load them as XTypes from local file system.
    AdvanceRemoteSchemaResolver
    Class to resolve schemas via in memory mapping.
    AdvanceTypeInference
    Utility class for the type inference.
    BuildJarRelease
    Creates a JAR file of the engine and a JAR file containing all dependencies.
